<em>Counter-Strike: Condition Zero</em> has been released and is available now via <a href="/?area=get_cz" target="_blank">Steam</a>. Those who pre-ordered the game via Steam can begin playing by double clicking the CS:CZ icon in their Steam Games list. For those who own Counter-Strike, Valve is offering a special price of $29.95 to those who purchase the game via Steam (Note: This offer will end at 11:59 pm PST on April 1, 2004). For more details, please visit <a href="/?area=get_cz" target="_blank">www.steampowered.com</a>.<br/></p>
